Title: Vae Victis
Description:
Ah it's time.

Kill their leader. Salt his bones, take his head, and laugh as his tribe crumbles!

Sharpscale's last moments are upon him, and he doesn't even realize it yet. 

Stupid fish-face.
ObjectivesText: Kill Sharpscale the Devourer and retrieve its head in the Hungering Pool in Hallowfall.
PortraitGiverText: Sharpscale has been terrorizing the Hungering Pool for some time.
CompletionText: His skull would make a good cup I think? Perhaps a mantle ornament?
RewardText:
Oh. This head is quite a bit more icky than I was expecting. You can keep that.

You are much more useful than I thought you would have been, $n.
